trans-unit.source: The NamedImagesCollection class represents a collection of <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImage> objects, which are objects that have an associated image and a name that is unique to the collection.
trans-unit.target: NamedImagesCollection 類別表示的集合<xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImage>物件，也就是具有相關聯的映像和集合的唯一名稱的物件。</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImage>

trans-unit.source: This class is exposed as the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.Images%2A> collection property of the root <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart> object, and is only available at run time.
trans-unit.target: 這個類別會公開為<xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.Images%2A>集合的根屬性<xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart>物件，並在執行階段才可用。</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.Images%2A>

trans-unit.source: An image can be any object derived from the .NET Framework <xref:System.Drawing.Image> class, such as <xref:System.Drawing.Bitmap>, which is created dynamically.
trans-unit.target: 影像可能是衍生自.NET Framework 的任何物件<xref:System.Drawing.Image>類別，例如<xref:System.Drawing.Bitmap>，這以動態方式建立。</xref:System.Drawing.Bitmap> </xref:System.Drawing.Image>

trans-unit.source: The image can be stored in this collection, and then assigned at a later time to any image property in the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart> control, such as <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.BackImage%2A>.
trans-unit.target: 可以儲存在這個集合，並接著指派至<xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart>控制項，例如<xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.BackImage%2A>.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.BackImage%2A></xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart>中任何映像屬性稍後映像

trans-unit.source: When one of the image properties in the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart> control is set by specifying a `string` value, the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.Images%2A> collection property, of type NamedImagesCollection, is first checked to see if an image with that name exists.
trans-unit.target: 當其中一個映像內容中<xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart>控制項設定所指定`string`值， <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.Images%2A>NamedImagesCollection，型別 集合屬性，會先檢查是否已有該名稱的映像。</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.Images%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart>

trans-unit.source: If a matching <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImage> object is found, this image is used.
trans-unit.target: 如果比對<xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImage>找不到物件，會使用此映像。</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImage>

trans-unit.source: If a matching <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImage> object is not located, the string expression is treated as a URL, image resource name or pathname.
trans-unit.target: 如果比對<xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImage>物件不是位於，字串運算式會被視為 URL、 映像資源名稱或路徑名稱。</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImage>
